  <p align="left"><b>13</b>	To encourage motivation teachersshould &#x2026;</p>
  <g id="t1">A.  hide any low expectations they may have of individual students.</g>
  <g id="t2">B.  create the appropriate atmosphere during the lesson.</g>
  <g id="t3">C.  reward students' efforts even when they fail.</g>
  <g id="t4">D.  tell students the reason for each exercise they do.</g>
  <g id="t5">E.  try to make learning fun.</g>
